{
  "id": "adv_card_ngs_08_03",
  "title": "伊吹渚",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "ついにゲームが出来たんですね",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "何か問題がないか、しっかりテストプレイしておこう",
      "startTime": 4.2999995549,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.7747164886
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　なんだか緊張しますね、えへへ\nそれじゃあ、ゲームスタート！",
      "startTime": 13.3080498219,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "ここは私が主人公と一緒に本を\n読んでいるシーン……",
      "startTime": 21.9413820108,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "う～……ゲームの中とはいえ、こんな雰囲気の中で\n好きな人と手を重ねるなんて……！",
      "startTime": 29.4080471516,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "でも、このシーンは主人公の照れ方も\n可愛くて好きなんですよね、えへへ",
      "startTime": 35.8413804849,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、今更なんですけど",
      "startTime": 39.9413807392,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "これって、私の理想の恋愛を詰め込んだゲームだって\n公表したりするんでしょうか……？",
      "startTime": 47.3747140725,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "その点に関しては、プロモーションとの兼ね合いも\nあるから要相談だな。渚はどうしたい？",
      "startTime": 52.3333360036,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "公表するのはちょっと恥ずかしい気が……あ、でも",
      "startTime": 55.9667857806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "もし公表しなかったら、{user}さん\nだけが事情を知ってるってことになるんですよね",
      "startTime": 65.2667857806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "それはそれで秘密の共有って感じがしてすっごく\n恥ずかしいかも！？　わー！ どうしよう……！？",
      "startTime": 73.4334524472,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "渚？　どうした、顔が真っ赤だぞ？",
      "startTime": 78.4667857806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "な、なんでもないです！\n公表の件は考えさせて下さーい！",
      "startTime": 84.700477858,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.2666731517
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ、やっとクリア出来ましたね",
      "startTime": 90.3933160146,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "実際にゲームとしてプレイしてみてどうだった？",
      "startTime": 94.2599826813,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.4720236143
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "なんていうか……ずっと不思議な感じでした",
      "startTime": 97.4720236143,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "初めは自分がモデルだと思うと、とにかく\n照れちゃって直視出来なかったんですけど……",
      "startTime": 105.538690281,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.5720236143
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "だんだん主人公に感情移入してきて、最後の方は\nとにかく二人の恋を応援してました",
      "startTime": 112.538690281,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.5053569477
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "夢中になれるということは、それだけいいゲーム\nだっていう証拠だと思うぞ。俺も楽しかったよ",
      "startTime": 118.3000049591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "いろんなルートがあるし、せっかくだから\n俺はもう少しプレイしてみるよ",
      "startTime": 124.7000049591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.8711874327
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました。感想、聞かせて下さいね",
      "startTime": 126.8711874327,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 131.6378602029,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1228.8063366000017,
          "startTime": 132.8666665395
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_way_night",
      "startTime": 132.7378540995
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-ngs017.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございまーす……あれ？\n{user}さん？",
      "startTime": 138.9711813293,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-ngs018.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、ゲームしたまま寝ちゃってる\n最近は休憩中ずっとプレイしてるって言ってたっけ",
      "startTime": 145.1045177144,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-ngs019.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか子供っぽい寝顔……可愛いなーもう",
      "startTime": 149.8045217833,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-ngs020.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、朝だよ？　{user}くん、起きて",
      "startTime": 157.1045197488,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "う……んん……？　渚か……おはよう",
      "startTime": 160.9711915017,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-ngs021.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、おはようございます",
      "startTime": 169.4334138712,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ゲームを夢中でプレイしてる内に寝てたみたいだ\nふわぁ～……",
      "startTime": 176.3666762034,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、ついさっきまでゲームをプレイしてた\nからかな。ゲームと同じセリフで起こされた気がしたよ",
      "startTime": 183.03334287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-ngs022.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？　あ、そ、そうなんですか？　あはは\nもう、現実と夢がごっちゃになってますよー？",
      "startTime": 192.1243684611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "なんでそんなに慌ててるんだ……ん？\nその服って、もしかして…………",
      "startTime": 200.4000125885,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-ngs023.m4a",
      "text": "あ、気付いちゃいました？\nこれ、ゲームの中の私が着てた服と同じなんです",
      "startTime": 206.1197428069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-ngs024.m4a",
      "text": "ゲームのプロモーション用にって\n衣装さんが同じ服を作ってくれたんですよ",
      "startTime": 212.553075123,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_08_03-ngs025.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ……似合ってますか？",
      "startTime": 215.8864084563,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
